<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<style>
    /* Reset some default browser styles */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

/* Basic layout */
body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 100vh;
}

/* Header styles */
header {
    background: #4CAF50;
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
}

nav .logo {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
}

nav .nav-links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
}

nav .nav-links a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
}

nav .nav-links a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

/* Section styles */
section {
    padding: 2rem;
}

section h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

section p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

/* Service cards */
.service-card {
    background: #f1f1f1;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    border-radius: 5px;
    text-align: center;
}

.service-card h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

/* Footer styles */
footer {
    background: #4CAF50;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-top: auto;
}

</style>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">Medicare</div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="services.html">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <section id="services">
            <h1>Our Services</h1>
            <div class="service-card">
                <h2>Primary Care</h2>
                <p>Comprehensive primary care services to keep you healthy. Our experienced doctors and healthcare professionals provide routine check-ups, vaccinations, and preventive care.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <h2>Specialty Care</h2>
                <p>Expert specialists for all your specific health needs. We offer specialized services in cardiology, neurology, orthopedics, and more to ensure you receive the best possible care.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <h2>Emergency Care</h2>
                <p>24/7 emergency care services for urgent health issues. Our emergency department is equipped to handle any medical emergency, providing immediate and effective treatment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <h2>Laboratory Services</h2>
                <p>State-of-the-art laboratory services for accurate and timely diagnosis. We offer a wide range of tests and screenings to help you stay informed about your health.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <h2>Pharmacy Services</h2>
                <p>Convenient pharmacy services to fulfill your medication needs. Our on-site pharmacy provides prescription medications, over-the-counter drugs, and professional advice.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Medicare. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>